== SOURCE
https://artificialintelligence-news.com/2020/08/10/darpa-ai-jet-fight-online-covid-19/
== AGENT
Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency
== GOAL
Hold four events to display and test AI-powered jet fighters virtually
== DATA
Simulating dog fights and try new and improved deep learning algorithms.
== METHODS
Designing, testing and improving different system AIs through dogfight championship in a round-robin tournament.
== RESULTS
Improved on dog fighting and AI flight training techniques.
== ISSUES
This is usually an event where people attend from all across the world, the event was held online this year due to Covid-19
== SCORE
8
== COMMENTS
The dog fighting simulations were really awesome to watch.